review.reviewBody:
27. Katsu Curry seems to be a smaller portion. I wish the curry sauce was thicker.
58. Kara! Karaage sauce was pretty good.
55. Takoyaki wasn crispy but thats probably because it was in a takeout box.
The food was good, I liked the 13. Steak Don , but they had my pickup order ready over 30 minutes too early.
Great food and our weekly go to comfort dishes.
Portions are super small! The container is less than half full.
The food tasted well but theres not much protein in the bowl, very little chicken in it...
